== Major Features == * '''Paved Stone Building''' – Late {{ill|Jomon period|ja|縄文時代}} * '''Ritual Site''' – {{ill|Yayoi period|ja|弥生時代}} * '''Settlement Transition''' – From the Yayoi to the Heian period * '''Miyayama Otsuka Kofun''' – Middle Kofun period (5th century), {{ill|Keyhole-shaped burial mound|ja|前方後円墳}}, with a posterior diameter of 40 meters and height of 6 meters, and a 6-meter-wide surrounding moat. * '''Mound 1''' – Circular tumulus with a {{ill|Yokoana-shiki sekishitsu|ja|横穴式石室}} (stone chamber), diameter of 20 meters, Late Kofun period * '''Mound 2''' – Circular tumulus with a stone chamber, Late Kofun period * '''Mound 3''' – Circular tumulus with a stone chamber, Late Kofun period * '''Mound 4''' – Circular tumulus with a stone chamber, Late Kofun period * '''Mound 5''' – Circular tumulus with a stone chamber, Late Kofun period * '''Mound 6''' – Circular tumulus with a stone chamber, Late Kofun period
