== Miyayama Rural Park == This park was developed under the national {{ill|Comprehensive Rural Development Model Project|ja|農村総合整備モデル事業|12=draft|12=draft}}. It features walking paths weaving between the mounds and a plaza area west of Miyayama Otsuka Kofun. The total area is 2,655.91 square meters.
